  "merger_description": "Precision Poultry Pty Ltd (**Precision Poultry**) proposes to acquire the broiler chicken farming operations of VOAG Pty Ltd and its related entities (**VOAG**) through coordinated asset and land acquisitions (the **Acquisition**).\n\nPursuant to the Acquisition, Precision Poultry will acquire:\n\n* broiler chicken farming business assets from VOAG Pty Ltd, and\n* the freehold land on which the farming assets are operated from subsidiaries of VOAG 6 Pty Ltd, the head landholder entity of the vendor, being VOAG 1 Pty Ltd, VOAG 2 Pty Ltd, VOAG 3 Pty Ltd, VOAG 4 Pty Ltd and VOAG 5 Pty Ltd.\n\nPrecision Poultry has been established as an investment vehicle by private equity firm Roc Partners to provide agribusiness investment returns to Roc Partners-controlled or managed entities.\n\nPrecision Poultry and VOAG both supply broiler chicken growing services. Precision Poultry\u2019s farming operations are located in Victoria. VOAG\u2019s farming operations are located in New South Wales. Both parties supply broiler chicken growing services to separate poultry meat processors in their respective regions.\n\nNeither the acquirer or the target entities (or their connected entities) engage in chicken breeding, hatchery operations, feed milling, poultry meat processing, or egg product production.",
